          "chunk_id": "0001045810-26-000056#s001#p1",
          "document_id": "0001045810-26-000056",
          "section_id": "s001",
          "paragraph_index": 1,
          "text": "On June 24, 2026, at the 2026 Annual Meeting of Stockholders of NVIDIA Corporation, or the 2026 Annual Meeting, the following proposals were adopted or rejected by the margin indicated.",
