          "document_id": "0001045810-26-000056",
          "section_id": "s001",
          "paragraph_index": 18,
          "text": "4. Stockholders approved the non-binding stockholder proposal to replace the supermajority voting provisions in our charter and bylaws with a simple majority voting standard. The results of the voting were as follows:",
          "chunk_type": "paragraph",
          "is_heading": false,
          "char_len": 217
        },
        {
